   |         ^^^^^^^
21 |         cls, *args: Any, **kwargs: Any
22 |     ) -> Bad: ...  # Y034 "__new__" methods usually return "self" at runtime. Consider using "typing_extensions.Self" in "Bad.__new__"…
   |
help: Use `Self` as return type
   |
